{"tid":903072,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"Cold call狗祝你老母俾狗屌","createTime":"2018-11-15T09:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T10:01:07.000Z","uid":44322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb0f2de4af1398bb6f4f814f737cab15dfccda8","tid":903072,"uid":44322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的，重個大半個鐘就收工緊係坐係位發下夢。無啦啦電話響又得個number<br />\n<br />\n(公司關係慣左唔知咩電話都照聽，又有一段時間無update Whoscall)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zm8LDh4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZm8LDh4.png&h=2bda05d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一聽，大新銀行，秒速cut線。<br />\n<br />\n幾秒後有個無來電打黎照聽（屋企電話係無來電），一聽對方即cut線，幾秒後又一個（已經估到係cold call條撚樣玩野）<br />\n<br />\n我直接cut。條撚樣又真係夠膽死連打幾個黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0pKTTk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0pKTTk.png&h=a8808816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次遇到咁撚夠薑既cold call狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458c7626802027773dd0e267796ea93aa9e30958","tid":903072,"uid":44322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d3085ea7ec211a729d41f5c58acf22d8f07b3e","tid":903072,"uid":44322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3626dc9a337532006f282fa0763ec0c3c0c3e8d7","tid":903072,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:48:46.000Z","msg":"我隔離同事黎，我代佢講唔好意思"},{"pid":"7a9aa27e15121f19456c581fcf090f58aef46f27","tid":903072,"uid":44322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3626dc9a337532006f282fa0763ec0c3c0c3e8d7","tid":903072,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T09:48:46.00